Title: Part 7: The Woodland Realms
Text:
I met Radagast the brown one. He warned me about all sorts of evil forces that are going on at the moment!
I should be careful on my journey to the Elves!
The forest is full of spiders. Also, I shouldn't leave the path, the dark magic there is playing with my mind!
CompleteText:
Finally a way out of the woods!
Here is the heart of the kingdom of the Wood Elves and the halls of King Thranduil.
Maybe he can help us with our mission!
